Fishnet Documentation

Overview

fish.h is the place where all public fishnet interfaces are defined. Look at the documentation for that file (or the comments in that file) for specific information.

Module Documentation

The fishnet documentation has been grouped into "modules" that should make it quicker to find documentation for the functionality you are looking for. The modules are:

  • L1 Functions and constants
  • L2 Functionality
  • ARP Functionality
  • L3 Functionality
  • Forwarding Table
  • FCMP Functions
  • Debugging functions
